            <div class='flex flex-col gap-2'>
              <span class='text-base font-bold text-neutral-2'>Jan 2022 - Present</span>
              <p class='text-neutral-2 text-base lg:!text-xl font-normal leading-7'>
                Maintenance and development of the different DrEnvio projects, refactoring, online
